                        <locus from="70r" to="78r">ff. 70r-78r</locus>
                        <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_21985">Naql-i kayfiyat-i mulāqāt-i Rājah Nihāl Singh bā Gavarnar Janral</title>
                        <title xml:lang="per" key="work_21985">نقل كيفيت ملاقات راجه نهال سنگه با گورنر جنرل</title>
                        <note>
                           <p>Account of the meeting with the unnamed (<persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164658646.0x000001 viaf_71381728" ref="http://lccn.loc.gov/n88175496" role="subject">Marquess of Dalhousie</persName>) Governor-General’s  on 7 November 1849 with <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164658544.0x000001 viaf_58218296" ref="http://lccn.loc.gov/n89297568" role="subject">Rājah Nihāl Singh Bahādur Ahlūvāliyah</persName>, with lists of those present, their presentational gifts, and the grant to each presenter of a ceremonial khilʿat
                           </p>
                           <p>The account reproduced (naql) here is attributed to the raja’s secretary, who is not identified by name
</p>
                           <p>Not dated</p>
                        </note>
                        <textLang mainLang="per">Persian</textLang>
                        <note/>
