                        <locus to="100r" from="97r">ff. 97r-100r</locus>
                        <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_21987">Rūḥ-i mashrūḥ</title>
                        <title xml:lang="per" key="work_21987">روح مشروح</title>
                        <note>
                           <p>Collection of the private letters addressed to the compiler, <persName key="person_f7431" role="rcp com">Munshī Gangā Bishan "Fikrat"</persName>, from <persName key="person_f7083" role="aut">Bābū Shīv Prashād</persName>, nabīrah (son’s son) of the late <persName key="person_f7493" role="oth">Rājah Dālchand</persName>, the sar'rishtah'dār of the Superintendent’s Office, Shimla
                           </p>
                           <p>The letters share the theme of discussions on ethics, comparative religion, and Sanskrit mantras
</p>
                           <p>Not dated
</p>
                           <p>Folios 101-2 left blank
</p>
                        </note>
                        <textLang mainLang="per" otherLangs="san">Persian</textLang>
